[SN]TITLE[SN]
Centrica shares dive 10% on fund raising move

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
(Close): Shares in British Gas owner Centrica sank nearly 10% after it announced plans to raise more capital through a share sale.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
